  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK564">
<l>iṟaikaṭiya ṉeṉṟuraikku miṉṉāccol vēnta </l>
<l> ṉuṟaikaṭuki yollaik keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The king who is spoken of as cruel will quickly perish his life becoming shortened.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
